# Project Overview

This is a Turborepo monorepo project with Next.js applications and shared packages.

## Project Structure
- **Applications** - Located in the [apps/](mdc:apps) directory
  - [Web Application](mdc:apps/web) - Main Next.js application
  - [Documentation](mdc:apps/docs) - Project documentation site
  
- **Shared Packages** - Located in the [packages/](mdc:packages) directory
  - [UI Components](mdc:packages/ui) - Shared UI components
  - [TypeScript Configuration](mdc:packages/typescript-config) - Shared TypeScript configurations
  - [Tailwind Configuration](mdc:packages/tailwind-config) - Shared Tailwind CSS setup
  - [ESLint Configuration](mdc:packages/eslint-config) - Shared ESLint rules

## Development Workflow
- `bun run dev` - Start development environment for all apps
- `bun run build` - Build all applications
- `bun run lint` - Run linting on all projects

